---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Community Life" description="Explore the vibrant community life of the Baháʼí Faith through core activities and service.">
  <Hero
    title="Community Life"
    subtitle="Building vibrant, unified communities through service and devotion"
  />

  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">The Core Activities</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Baháʼí community life revolves around core activities that foster spiritual growth, build community bonds, and contribute to social transformation. These activities are open to all, regardless of background or belief.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Study Circles</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Small groups that study the Ruhi Institute books, exploring spiritual concepts and developing capacity for service to humanity.
            </p>
            <a href="/study" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">Learn More →</a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Devotional Gatherings</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Regular gatherings where people come together for prayer, meditation, and spiritual reflection in a spirit of fellowship.
            </p>
            <a href="/devotional" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">Learn More →</a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Children's Classes</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Spiritual education classes for children aged 5-10, helping them develop noble character and spiritual qualities.
            </p>
            <a href="/events" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">Find a Class →</a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Junior Youth Groups</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Empowerment program for ages 11-14, helping young people navigate a crucial stage of life with spiritual strength.
            </p>
            <a href="/events" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">Join a Group →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Nineteen Day Feast</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            The Nineteen Day Feast is the principal gathering of the Baháʼí community at the local level. Held once every Baháʼí month (every 19 days), it brings together Baháʼís for worship, consultation, and fellowship.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            The Feast has three parts: a devotional portion with prayers and readings, a consultative portion for community business and planning, and a social portion for fellowship and hospitality.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-8 border border-blue-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Get Involved</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Everyone is welcome to participate in our community activities. Whether you're new to the Faith or simply curious, we invite you to join us.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <a href="/events" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium transition">
              View Events
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 text-blue-600 border-2 border-blue-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium transition">
              Contact Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
